questions.statement:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;Select the option that is related to the third number in the same way as the second number is related to the first number.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;span data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;-9/11 : 11/9 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;∷&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt; 13/2 : ?&lt;/span&gt;<br>&lt;p&gt;उस विकल्प का चयन कीजिये जो तीसरी संख्या से उसी तरह से संबंधित है जिस प्रकार दूसरी संख्या पहली संख्या से संबंधित है।&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;span data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;-9/11 : 11/9 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;∷&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt; 13/2 : ?&lt;/span&gt;

questions.explanation:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;The logic is:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;-9/11 : 11/9 &amp;rarr; -9/11 : -1 &amp;divide; (-9/11)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;Similarly,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;13/2 : ? &amp;rarr; 13/2 : -1 &amp;divide; (13/2)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr;&lt;span data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt; ? = -2/13&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;span data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;Hence, &amp;lsquo;-2/13&amp;rsquo; is the correct answer.&lt;/span&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-darkreader-inline-bgcolor=&quot;&quot; data-darkreader-inline-bgimage=&quot;&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;दिया&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span data-darkreader-inline-bgcolor=&quot;&quot; data-darkreader-inline-bgimage=&quot;&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;गया&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span data-darkreader-inline-bgcolor=&quot;&quot; data-darkreader-inline-bgimage=&quot;&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;तर्क&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span data-darkreader-inline-bgcolor=&quot;&quot; data-darkreader-inline-bgimage=&quot;&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;निम्न&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span data-darkreader-inline-bgcolor=&quot;&quot; data-darkreader-inline-bgimage=&quot;&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;प्रकार&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span data-darkreader-inline-bgcolor=&quot;&quot; data-darkreader-inline-bgimage=&quot;&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;है&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-darkreader-inline-bgcolor=&quot;&quot; data-darkreader-inline-bgimage=&quot;&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;-9/11 : 11/9 &amp;rarr; -9/11 : -1 &amp;divide; (-9/11)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;इसी&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;तरह&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;13/2 : ? &amp;rarr; 13/2 : -1 &amp;divide; (13/2)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr;&lt;span data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt; ? = -2/13&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;span data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;अतः&lt;/span&gt; &amp;lsquo;-2/13&amp;rsquo; सही उत्तर है।

