Hence, the pilgrim is 5 km to the north with respect to her starting position.<br><br>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/20/07/F1_A.M_Shraddha_25.06.2020_7.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 550px; height: 425px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
